title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J Kaiser Convention Center on 1987-11-06
description:
Set 1

Big Boss Man, Feel Like A Stranger, It Must Have Been The Roses, Minglewood Blues, When Push Comes To Shove, Me & My Uncle-> Cumberland Blues, Let It Grow

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Hell In A Bucket, He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Morning Dew-> All Along The Watchtower, E: Black Muddy River

Rex Benefit"We Want Phil" chantRex Benefit *Lights went on, crowd wouldn't leave.Band came back
